    <h1>terms and conditions</h1>\
    <h2>A legal agreement</h2>
    <p>The phrase signals that there is a contract, often called Terms of Service or Terms of Use, which users agree to by using the service or accepting the offer</p>
   <hr>
    <h2>Rules and limitations</h2>
    <p>It means the offer or service operates under a specific set of rules, which can include things like eligibility, usage restrictions, intellectual property rights, and payment details</p>
    <hr>
    <h2>User responsibilities</h2>
    <p>For the user, it means they must abide by the rules to continue using the service or to take advantage of the offer. </p>
    <hr>
